a:title><![CDATA[53rd annual UFO Encounter in Roswell, New Mexico]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The ChatGPT app is now available for Android]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> OpenAI 言出必行。 <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/chatgpts-android-app-arrives-in-the-last-week-of-july-075639727.html">正如承诺的那样</a>，该公司<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3BsYXkuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS9zdG9yZS9hcHBzL2RldGFpbHM_aWQ9Y29tLm9wZW5haS5jaGF0Z3B0IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIwYjNlY2UzMi02ZGJjLTQ2NWUtODczMi1mZDJmODc3NTE2YTkifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAVHsUoXq2MExl0-_Op2VUFpFcBdyMeKD8qCnQDToSeTr&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.openai.chatgpt" class="rapid-with-clickid">发布了</a>Android 版 ChatGPT 应用程序。与<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/chatgpt-now-has-an-official-iphone-app-181454446.html">iOS 版本</a>一样，您可以与生成人工智能对话以获得建议、答案和其他（希望如此）有用的回复。您可以使用 OpenAI 的内部语音识别发出语音请求，跨设备同步聊天历史记录并导出数据 - 您将主要错过<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/chatgpts-new-plugins-will-deliver-real-time-stats-182900388.html">插件</a>。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/openai-chatgpt-plus-subscription-205027758.html">ChatGPT Plus</a>订阅者还可以随意在标准（GPT-3.5）和 GPT-4 语言模型之间切换。无论您使用哪个级别，您至少需要 Android 6.0 才能使用该应用程序。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>该应用程序可以使 ChatGPT 更容易使用，特别是在 Android 占主导地位或 PC 不太常见的国家。该软件自 5 月份起就向 iPhone 用户提供，随后更新了 iPad 支持。</p><p>与 Bing Chat（基于 GPT-4）、Bard 和其他对话式 AI 系统一样，您不会希望完全依赖结果。该技术很容易产生“幻觉”，从而导致虚假声明、糟糕的上下文逻辑和其他不值得信赖的输出。有时，ChatGPT 作为任务的起点比获得明确的答案更有用，并且可以帮助完成准确性不那么重要的创造性任务。</p><p> OpenAI 通过 ChatGPT 等工具帮助普及了生成式人工智能，但它也导致了行业的抵制和政治关注。专家担心这样的技术<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ai-pioneer-geoffrey-hinton-isnt-convinced-good-ai-will-triumph-over-bad-ai-181536702.html">可能会控制或传播错误信息</a>，而 OpenAI 本身希望<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/openai-is-forming-a-team-to-rein-in-superintelligent-ai-214333388.html">减轻智能人工智能的风险</a>。美国演员罢工的部分原因是担心<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/striking-actors-say-rejected-ai-proposal-would-let-studios-use-their-likeness-without-fair-pay-000025878.html">制片厂可能会利用人工智能</a>来压制他们的片酬。与此同时，政治家们正在迫切要求<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/white-house-reveals-its-next-steps-towards-responsible-ai-development-190636857.html">负责任的发展</a>和可能的监管。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-chatgpt-app-is-now-available-for-android-163607202.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-chatgpt-app-is-now-available-for-android-163607202.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 0b3ece32-6dbc-465e-8732-fd2f877516a9</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jul 2023 16:36:07 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690304239</ingested><modified> 2023-07-25T16:57:21+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Mobile Apps]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1138" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/53404370-2b07-11ee-9ffb-78409eb78186" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></m